@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
[*] --> Draft
Draft --> Cancelled : approve
Cancelled --> OnHold : cancel
OnHold --> Pending : approve
Pending --> Delivered : reject
Delivered --> Archived : process
Delivered : entry / log warehouse
Archived --> [*]
@enduml